definition: Qingyang prefecture level city in Gansu

sentences.english: This training has been created by VSO volunteers in association with the Qingyang Education Bureau.
sentences.chinese: 本次培訓由VSO志願者和慶陽市教育局合作完成。

sentences.english: Characteristic agriculture is the major industrialization in Qingyang local economic development.
sentences.chinese: 特色農產品產業是慶陽市發展地方經濟的主導產業。

sentences.english: Qingyang municipal inland areas in the Middle Yellow River.
sentences.chinese: 慶陽市屬黃河中游內陸地區。
